message: Gotye tops us music charts for its second week of release. The singer-songwriter performed eight of the 12 songs on her latest album Last Kiss, which comes to us via iTunes. And, as previously reported, it was another strong run for the rapper. "This has been a long time coming, so I feel good," he said about the last few months leading up to the release of Last Kiss. Last Kiss is available now from iTunes in 45 countries. In the U.S., its tracklist includes "Runaround," featuring Rick Ross, and "I Got You Babe," featuring Drake.
